Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 对方的要求是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:15.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「未支付的报酬 外加50%的滞纳金
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共计750万美元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:22.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以现金或是金块的形式 在今天之内交付」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:25.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先不说金额 给的时间也太少了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:30.34,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也许他们从一开始就没有想交涉的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:31.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说他们只是为了杀鸡儆猴 就会杀了那个男的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就为了区区750万美元？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:39.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:43.73,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}估计他们并不知道人质的真实身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.73,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说到底为什么会沦落到这种局面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是一开始就遵守和他们的合同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会演变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:01.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柳井董事 现在可不是清点责任的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:07.29,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下 如何解决这一事态是更优先的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们公司不能失去他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:46.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早 伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又刷新了这条路线的记录？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:59.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这倒是挺厉害 不过安全系统发动的次数太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可是公路 驾驶时多小心一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系 入学至今没出过事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说回来 今天来我们班的转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说是个男生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:20.95,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:22.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这反应太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可是邂逅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一个小小的大事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:29.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是小还是大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还是提不起兴趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:37.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然转入了我们班 那肯定是个怪咖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:42.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别连着自己一起黑好不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:57.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:03.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对方擅自设下的时限根本毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这样的话人质就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有这个办法了 柳井董事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您可知道世界上有多少雾科的挖掘场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但现在给抓住的可是你们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论是谁都不能区别对待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总裁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:29.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:36.90,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚讨论的一事现在还不算是案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是业务上的小麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:44.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还请各位千万不要向外走漏风声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}濑良老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.89,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早上好 校长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保安部和工会也会冲我发火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.15,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.61,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这点怨言也就限于今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快要完成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:34.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}SWNPR方程式用试制2号机 X-2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:38.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}装载了比X-1提高了5%的动力和比冲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改良型SWNPR引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.01,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最高时速25万公里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.22,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有了它 下一期的竞速中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.89,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们就能创下史无前例的赛道记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:53.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真希望能在我任职期间看它飞上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十分抱歉 目前还没能确保其安全性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.73,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.53,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全是第一位的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}考虑到测试飞行员身上的负担 这也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实我是最想驾驶它的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还对当飞行员恋恋不舍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我毫不后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.46,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我现在有了新的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.76,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}新的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:26.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}培养未来的工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:35.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一起在宇宙航天产业里掀起新的革新 这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这也是校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 是笹山部长您的话鼓励了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦？我说过那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您说「人本身就是宝物」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.95,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「培育人才
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是建起支撑企业 社会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乃至世界的擎天巨柱」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真让人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一想到从A-TEC中会走出第二第三个濑良海斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不不 我和他们就没差几年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实打实的现役选手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}糟了 该开晨会了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好 我是笹山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没事 现在我有空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么他现在抵达了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:34.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各…各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:44.13,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说我们的特别节目是在今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.00,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.55,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是好好宣传了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:51.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看到我们造出的机器 肯定都要吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真想快点进行试飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位 你们这样由奈很为难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.11,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好听她说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老师也说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎？啊…这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关于预算这件事 我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次班会上再认真讨论下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么晨会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个最会浪费的行家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:29.13,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里可能真是怪咖班…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 海斗亲 还有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在教室里要喊我老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别说这个了 那个要来的转校生怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:41.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:45.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他好像迟到了 所以还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我记得他是木卫三来的归国子女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.95,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是出境时出了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等下 你说的我还第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么连这都知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:58.54,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该说是我们只知道这点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想要接触转校生的人事信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但安全等级太高 我是彻底束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过是个转校生 这也太不寻常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又干这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.55,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在我们班这里也要特殊对待他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别刨根问底了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作吾 泄露机密可会受惩戒处分的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:23.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}算了吧老师 这只是安全检查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我每次找到安全漏洞的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不都会连对策都加上 提交报告的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是说这个 而是说你们的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你听好 同学们也听清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们的确是雾科公司选拔出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}换句话说就是精英生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过不要进了这个班就自恃甚高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你们在身为这A-TEC的一员之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:55.55,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先是雾科学园 乃至雾科集团的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.51,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然你们是我的学生 就给我扔掉精英观念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.89,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要把同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:01.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把职员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.31,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把在这雾科工作的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全都当做家人来对待！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又开始唠嗑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.53,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当自己昭和年代的工薪族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我哥哥这话匣子一开就停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来 跟我复述
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「谦虚 诚实 正直」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 就这样谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.46,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们现在正与你所属的公司做交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然对你多有不便 还请再忍耐一会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:40.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们会保证你的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过只有你们公司老实答应交易才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:49.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}转校生被抓了当人质？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道Coldwood吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是那颗资源型小行星？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:59.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 雾科在那边出资建有氦-3挖掘场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但公司与那边的工作人员在酬劳上起了争执
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把他给卷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可他为什么会在那么危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他父母是和雾科有关系的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其实这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:23.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对方要求获得当初定下的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果拿不到钱就灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那赶紧把钱付了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说到底都怪雾科欠薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:36.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多亏柳井副总裁的决定 支付上有了眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是事情没有这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个挖掘场决定要关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}银行也撤离了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:49.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且他们连户头都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是一群按天算钱的雇工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那该怎么付钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:59.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说他们的条件是要求以现金或金块的方式送到当地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且今天之内就要送到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.18,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太荒唐了 只剩8个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以一般的航线…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 等一下 我记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这样 濑良老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:23.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不要告诉学生这件事 就交给你定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但请不要因此而太过不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:27.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能赶上！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走这条路线的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}濑良老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很遗憾 公司是不会满足你们的要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:43.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摆出这种态度可不是聪明人该干的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们的做法没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是选错人质了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.69,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别慌 只是张名片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:04.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:09.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如你所见 我在那个公司里的立场比较微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公司里也有想把你们的提案连着我的存在一起抹消掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们最好小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是要恐吓我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 我是在和你们谈生意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不来一起考虑下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们全员都能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.35,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并且都能获益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}双赢的解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这样 为了救出转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:41.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须在今天之内将现金送至当地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天之内…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到Coldwood紧赶慢赶至少也要13小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没戏 这绝对没戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 应该是没戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.25,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}…对于我们以外的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么意思 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.71,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.13,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:01.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后把转校生带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.47,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用上X-2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说什么呢 海斗亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连试飞都还没做过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是你自己说还得花两周调整的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且老师至今为止一次都没飞过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧 我以前还参加过竞速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有国际B级执照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是多少年前的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}偶尔相信下老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除了我们的X-2外就别无他法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们一起去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:40.50,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为哥哥你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像这样 到Coldwood的路线绕了一个大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.81,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想在今天内到达是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我们走这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}距离约为原始线路的三分之二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}靠我们这台机器 能在今天内到达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.78,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.62,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 您画出的这条路线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:17.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像若无其事地经过了禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:23.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个…所以说 有我们A-TEC优秀的机组人员支援的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一两个禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没戏！绝对没戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是我们的皇牌也没戏！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我 濑良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这里是管制室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.90,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您这让我很困扰啊 濑良室长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊？什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:54.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}起飞？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:56.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿你没辙 今天帮你搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.79,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下次麻烦在两天前申请啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:07.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 所以你到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每次都太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:28.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说回来 我们真的有执行解救人质作战的权限吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这明显是牵扯全公司的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上头还没动静 我们擅自行动果然还是不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.62,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起这些 现在最不妙的是伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道是哪个神经大条的哥哥整出来的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起 我完全没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能听到吗 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去救转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.10,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要去的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才是正规机师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.56,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能交给外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别想着要维护我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.69,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没这样想过 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唔…你这么干脆地否定还是有点小受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 美月在担心老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊 伊莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.66,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快停下 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.83,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}预定路线上的禁止航行宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:27.00,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是小行星带！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.96,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么不早说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.05,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}启动系统吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}All systems go！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}影像来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}X-2 请你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没问题 通过密集地带了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}情况怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.17,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}左侧辅助推进器装甲破损
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目前对航行不构成影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.39,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.77,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个推进器的装甲部件是特别定制的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.60,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.44,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}破损部位出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.40,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现将推进器分离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.86,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知不知道这个推进器有多贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是 老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:41.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别管了 动手吧 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.16,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:47.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安全第一 任务第二 没有三四 代价第五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:48.92,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:57.38,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}8亿块的推进器…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}确认到Coldwood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:16.03,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}预计到达时间 2355
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们做的引擎果然是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.75,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毕竟得了海斗老师直传
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.12,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伊莉丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.67,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}X-2 请报告损坏情况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.88,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}预备燃料罐严重损毁 已经分离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷却器部分破损
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:50.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}2亿5千万…3亿…6亿8千万…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}干得好 白崎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后就是进入屋子运输升降口 交付钱款
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:58.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Copy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:01.20,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了 千万不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.37,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先给他们看钱 表现你没有无抵抗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.50,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}着陆系统不工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.33,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作吾 知道原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.42,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只知道修复需要不少时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.84,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.34,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明早之前肯定可以修好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白崎 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在我们这边在着手修复系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:36.07,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放心吧 肯定能修好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.65,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:41.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先暂且绕Coldwood环行 等待下一个指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.74,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂等下 白崎 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:47.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.08,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不是没什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.04,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是打算冲进去吧 是这样对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.46,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以这机体的状况 不可能冲得进去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是转校生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绑架犯们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么没人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:01.99,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才要问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.72,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在人类仍然对宇宙心怀憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.93,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}充满开拓者精神的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.14,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太阳系各行星都被「地球化」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:35.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无数人们在其上安居乐业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:40.27,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火星便是其中的一个行星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上面散布着各个国家的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个故事便是以在其上筑建起的日本新的都道府县之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.82,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「第四东京都」为舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:56.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}年轻的高中上班族们所描绘出的青春涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是这个A-TEC的领队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.30,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个嘛…我是班主任濑良
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:13.43,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说 是你昨天指挥的解救人质行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我 那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是糟糕至极的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:23.94,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这地方比传闻里说的还累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.32,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也明白为什么老哥要叹气了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我等下 你什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:30.41,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.28,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们浪费了太多资金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:33.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}资 资金？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:38.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本次解救行动的支出为5亿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:43.80,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}加上行动之后的机械和系统维护费
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.63,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还要追加5亿左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.97,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这都只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:55.64,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次严重损毁的试作机的开发费用 总额为150亿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:59.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你以为这是赎金的多少倍？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.48,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:07.49,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在说存在对我见死不救这个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:11.70,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 在那情况下这才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:16.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:21.58,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}近几年来你们A-TEC每年的预算超过500亿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:26.21,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从我们公司的规模来说也是不能忽略的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:29.26,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.09,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:38.52,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾科公司 前沿技术开发部部长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾羽渚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:47.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}转校生是…我们的上司？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.19,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.24,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道你是社长的同族？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.32,0:23:58.45,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我身上的任务是将你们A-TEC解体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:01.87,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是裁了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:10.13,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.97,0:24:12.59,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今开始请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:17.85,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂喂 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:21.06,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最多只能再留这组织一年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:22.23,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然是来真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:23.98,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吐槽就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:26.36,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎呀 真是太棒了 濑良老师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.02,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.23,0:24:29.57,Theme CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这下头疼了
